      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here are 5 **High-Protein Meal Prep Ideas** for your family of 4:\n\n**1. Turkey & Quinoa Bowls** (35g protein)\n- CO2: 0.92 kg/serving\n- Prep time: 45 min for 8 servings\n- Cost: $3.50/serving\n\n**2. Greek Chicken Salad Jars** (28g protein)\n- CO2: 0.68 kg/serving\n- Prep time: 30 min for 8 jars\n- Cost: $4.00/serving\n\n**3. Lentil & Sweet Potato Curry** (22g protein)\n- CO2: 0.38 kg/serving\n- Prep time: 40 min for 8 servings\n- Cost: $2.20/serving\n\n**4. Egg & Black Bean Burritos** (24g protein)\n- CO2: 0.45 kg/serving\n- Prep time: 35 min for 16 burritos\n- Cost: $1.80/serving\n\n**5. Salmon & Veggie Foil Packs** (32g protein)\n- CO2: 1.2 kg/serving\n- Prep time: 25 min for 8 packs\n- Cost: $5.50/serving\n\n**Weekly CO2 Savings:** Choosing #3 twice saves 4.2 kg CO2 vs beef options!",
      "type": "text",
      "data": null
