    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Lentil & Sweet Potato Curry** - 8 servings\n\n**Ingredients:**\n- Red lentils 400g\n- Sweet potatoes 600g (cubed)\n- Coconut milk 400ml\n- Diced tomatoes 400g\n- Onion 200g, Garlic 15g, Ginger 10g\n- Curry powder 15g, Turmeric 5g, Cumin 5g\n- Spinach 150g\n- Rice 400g (serve on side)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Saute onion, garlic, ginger (5 min)\n2. Add spices, toast 1 min\n3. Add tomatoes, coconut milk, lentils, sweet potato\n4. Simmer 25 min until lentils soft\n5. Stir in spinach at the end\n6. Season to taste\n\n**Meal Prep Tips:**\n- Store in 8 glass containers\n- Freezes well up to 3 months\n- Reheat with splash of water\n\n**Nutrition per serving:** 380 cal, 22g protein, 12g fiber\n**CO2 per serving:** 0.38 kg (85% below average!)",
      "type": "recipe",
